'''溴化銅'''是一种无机化合物，为二价[[銅|銅]]的[[溴化物|溴化物]]，化学式CuBr<sub>2</sub>。

==制备==
溴化铜可由[[氧化铜|氧化铜]]和[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]反应得到：<ref>{{cite book |title=Synthetic methods of Organometallic and Inorganic Chemistry |editor1-first=D. K. |editor1-last=Breitinger |editor2-first=W. A. |editor2-last=Herrmann |publisher=Thieme Medical Publishers |publicationplace=New York |year=1999 |isbn=0-86577-662-8}}</ref>
: CuO + 2 HBr → CuBr<sub>2</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O

==结构及性质==
在固态，CuBr<sub>2</sub>有着聚合结构，其中[CuBr<sub>4</sub>]平面单元对侧链接以形成链。CuBr<sub>2</sub>晶体属[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]，[[空间群|空间群]]C2/m，[[晶胞参数|晶胞参数]]a=714 pm, b=346 pm, c=718 pm, β=121°15′。<ref>{{cite journal |last=Helmholz |first=Lindsay |title=The Crystal Structure of Anhydrous Cupric Bromide |journal=[[Journal_of_the_American_Chemical_Society|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] |year=1947 |volume=69 |number=4 |pages=886–889 |doi=10.1021/ja01196a046}}</ref>CuBr<sub>2</sub>在高温时的气相为单分子。<ref>{{cite encyclopedia |last=Conry |first=Rebecca R. |article=Copper: Inorganic & Coordination Chemistry |title=Encyclopedia of Inorganic Chemistry |edition=2nd |publisher=John Wiley & Sons |year=2006 |doi=10.1002/0470862106.ia052 |isbn=978-0-470-86210-0}}</ref>

溴化铜和其它溴化物反应，可以得到多种铜溴配合物，如CsCuBr<sub>3</sub>、(EtNH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>Cu<sub>3</sub>Br<sub>8</sub>等。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Fletcher|first1=R.|last2=Hansen|first2=J. J.|last3=Livermore|first3=J.|last4=Willett|first4=R. D.|title=Crystal structure and magnetic properties of [(C2H5)2NH2]2(Cu3Br8).CuBr2.C2H5OH: magnetostructural correlations in copper(II) bromide salts|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=22|issue=2|year=1983|pages=330–334|issn=0020-1669|doi=10.1021/ic00144a025}}</ref>

